       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6CL03.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-INPUTS.
           05  WS-ELAPSED-DAYS       PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-NONWORKING-DAYS    PIC 9(3) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-CALCULATION.
           05  WS-ACCRUAL-DAYS       PIC S9(5) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-PENALTY-AMT        PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-ELAPSED-DAYS
           ACCEPT WS-NONWORKING-DAYS
           PERFORM 2200-APPLY-DAY-BASIS
           DISPLAY WS-PENALTY-AMT
           STOP RUN.
       2200-APPLY-DAY-BASIS.
           MOVE WS-ELAPSED-DAYS TO WS-ACCRUAL-DAYS
           EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN WS-NONWORKING-DAYS > ZERO
                 SUBTRACT WS-NONWORKING-DAYS FROM WS-ACCRUAL-DAYS
              WHEN OTHER
                 CONTINUE
           END-EVALUATE
           SUBTRACT 7 FROM WS-ACCRUAL-DAYS
           IF WS-ACCRUAL-DAYS > ZERO
              MULTIPLY 500 BY WS-ACCRUAL-DAYS
                 GIVING WS-PENALTY-AMT
           END-IF.
